## Import



antiddos cc_precision_policy can be imported using the id, e.g.

```sh
 $ pulumi import tencentcloud:Antiddos/ccPrecisionPolicy:CcPrecisionPolicy cc_precision_policy ${instanceId}#${policyId}#${instanceIp}#${domain}#${protocol}
```
